/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直頭轉名啦，第日佢老豆迫嫲嫲改咪又麻煩"},{"pid":"c5b567903898eafa4f75f9a054e9e1f37e9c3370","tid":500573,"uid":41616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 今晚約埋大表姑媽即刻報警<br />\n我唔會比呢個人渣得逞"},{"pid":"07b3544c8bc89528b0ff18ad8c607ee016af3c32","tid":500573,"uid":41616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"想問下報警應該點樣講 警察會用最快速度做野"},{"pid":"661c09a883496c85f8e28fcc702bdf7f4be8bd84","tid":500573,"uid":41616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下報警應該點樣講 警察會用最快速度做野</blockquote><br />\n我最撚驚係佢會唔知點樣整死阿嫲"},{"pid":"2ce380d6a9fd0c8bcdd44f2468dc7e81d5604d08","tid":500573,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下報警應該點樣講 警察會用最快速度做野</blockquote><br />\n你話你嫲嫲中左風之後比你老豆帶走左，依家間居都霸埋，你好擔心佢安全"},{"pid":"7634c7829b9626647daa4c2d551e7fd68070fdf9","tid":500573,"uid":50862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"搵私家偵探查<br />\n呢D有特定場所, 有哂Record<br />\n唔難查到"},{"pid":"7ae76b5df0a241faa479edda0f8469d64afdec48","tid":500573,"uid":14014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"直接報警話失左蹤 過左48<br />\n只係知入左老人院"},{"pid":"ae6ee2e3447d3ceb4d8e362bb981c66b7d06aade","tid":500573,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接報警話失左蹤 過左48<br />\n只係知入左老人院</blockquote><br />\n係要答咩都唔知，只知佢失左蹤，好擔心"},{"pid":"d6ca4f32f34e604ee79072385ce8d59952c92409","tid":500573,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"個老人家精神狀況如何<br />\n中風對佢認知有無影響"},{"pid":"b993ff56cd536bbf856ad14a819a7ea7b6924888","tid":500573,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下